  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Expand Your Influence. </h2><br>Increase the reach of your power by placing urns <br>to control diverse and strategically interesting defenses. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909090/extras/f5b32a6350242efe5fcd266e385ea466.apng?t=1727089321\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909090/extras/f5b32a6350242efe5fcd266e385ea466.poster.avif?t=1727089321\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=96 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Manage Your Wealth. </h2><br>Carefully manage risk and reward with an economy system where your very life depends<br>on the gold in your possession. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909090/extras/104b301b42dac03c804de9b8180e7c6a.poster.avif?t=1727089321\" width=96 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909090/extras/104b301b42dac03c804de9b8180e7c6a.webm?t=1727089321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reclaim What Was Stolen. </h2><br>Adventure through four modern museums reclaiming what was once yours with the gods watching your progress. <br><br>Or play individual levels freely with all unlocks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909090/extras/93faf54c9cb4f3409f23e7340094ddab.apng?t=1727089321\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909090/extras/93faf54c9cb4f3409f23e7340094ddab.poster.avif?t=1727089321\" class=\"bb_img\" width=96 height=96 /></picture></span>",
